com.alohar.user.content.data
Class UserStay

java.lang.Object
  com.alohar.user.content.data.UserStay
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class UserStay
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

An alohar detected visit of a place. It has a detected centroid (centroidLatE6, centroidLngE6), arrival time and departure time (in seconds), a selected place and a list of place candidates sorted by its ranking.

Author:
jianmingzhou
